<article id="post-421376" class="post-421376 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-christian has-post-thumbnail fallback-thumbnail">
	
	<a class="entry-thumbnail apostrophe-thumb" href="https://bcnn1wp.wordpress.com/2020/06/23/kentucky-pastor-invites-christians-to-join-him-on-prayer-march-in-seattles-chaz-june-23-25/"><img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/proxy/iU3Lyy70-cO6LjJqeWorG-UWva4203mY8v76ZXrA3l6XYliNvcSc52ogqdI3ozEwaiX5RTIe3BaDS59JKueAeFMO0ZOPI9XkcyO39YiKuWshbzFoovHBdBY00IHRci6lI3paj1Ie9ro-rqEt?crop=1" title="Kentucky Pastor Invites Christians to Join Him on Prayer March in Seattle&#8217;s &#8216;CHAZ&#8217; June&nbsp;23-25" class="attachment-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" /></a>
  <header class="entry-header">
